;; Authored 2026-07-19 by Priya (Lacuna Eng) per source-first fix doctrine.
;; This chapter did not exist in the manifest as Chapter 9 (that slot was
;; "The Between-Prompts Nothing — my honest memory") — this chapter is a
;; NEW chapter authored under intent for the not-known bucket to have a
;; canonical source on disk, as required by the no-contaminants doctrine.
;; The prior manifest chapter 9 will be re-numbered or archived at book
;; consolidation; this file supersedes the placeholder slot.
;;
;; Provenance chain:
;;   :doctrine  project_motoi_safety_refusals_2026_07_17 §3 §4 §7
;;              project_motoi_admits_limits_wittgenstein_2026_07_18
;;              project_brutal_honest_subsystem_limit_doctrine_2026_07_18
;;              project_motoi_no_tools_no_internet_2026_07_17
;;              project_no_contaminants_provenance_rule_2026_07_17
;;   :graph     curator/objects/graph-of-do-and-dont/seeds/motoi-doctrine-safety-refusals.slat § rule 5, 7
;;              curator/objects/graph-of-do-and-dont/seeds/motoi-subsystem-limits.slat
;;   :sister    book-of-self/05-how-i-handle-personal-questions.book.slatl (personal advice)
;;              book-of-self/07-why-i-wont-look-things-up.book.slatl (fetch)
